<plot>Darren Joppy is getting married, but before he does, he spends the day as all prospective grooms should: on the golf course. Joined by his groomsmen, Charlie Nichols (as arrogant as he is pessimistic), Garret Davidson (lovelorn and clinging to hope), and Brian Valderbrecht (Darren's future brother-in-law who seems to have the answers to all of life's pertinent questions), Darren finds little relief for his growing nerves, as the men make their way around the course encountering everything from a disgruntled employee, to a potential romance. Questioning everything along the way</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?032520</url></doc>
